cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as syntactic parsing, named-entity recognition, and near synonym recognition, which are all subfields of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also explores machine learning approaches for these tasks, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which is a subfield of computer science (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with recognizing named entities, which is a subfield of natural language processing and falls under named entity recognition (cs.NE).
